title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Wadding, Felt & Nonwovens, Special Yarns
description: Imports Intra Eu - Wadding, Felt & Nonwovens, Special Yarns in the United Kingdom increased to 37.36 GBP Million in September from 34.92 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Wadding, Felt & Nonwovens, Spec in the United Kingdom averaged 25.69 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 46.81 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 8.20 GBP Million in March of 2015. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Wadding, Felt & Nonwovens,.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
